Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.36,0:00:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,別以為我們會對學妹手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.97,0:00:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,誰怕誰 贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不會輸~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.37,0:00:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅 真要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.55,0:00:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 真的真的要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.92,0:01:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.27,0:01:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.70,0:01:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡享受和古蕾雅的二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.23,0:01:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,好浪漫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.24,0:01:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說些什麼呀 安
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 既然看了美景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.26,0:01:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.21,0:01:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 就在前面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,等著瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:02:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,古…古蕾雅 我們還是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.09,0:02:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,來都來了 你還抱怨什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能和古蕾雅單獨在一起很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很幸福…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.94,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我都沒法走了 安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真能回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.58,0:02:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你在摸哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒摸你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 這還是安提出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們一起過夜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.38,0:02:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.66,0:02:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說星星很美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,再一起放煙火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就睡在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.73,0:03:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.11,0:03:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我帶了成對的睡衣來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.25,0:03:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好 就這麼定了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.91,0:03:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.01,0:03:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是塊好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真虧你知道這裡 古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有人會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.56,0:04:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我在用沙子堆城堡 古蕾雅也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,安也快脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.26,0:04:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,別可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那古蕾雅幫我脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,打得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.06,0:05:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我還沒動真格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這次可要正式開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,開始什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.71,0:05:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你還要練習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,都是安說不好意思讓大家知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.31,0:05:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我們才來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,來 快脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,脫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.38,0:05:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.91,0:06:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,安 不能用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,憑什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.45,0:06:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就算游不了泳我可是能在水上行走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.32,0:07:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 有我在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我的腳已經碰不到地了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.67,0:07:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,先試著自己浮起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,浮？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,人類可無法浮在水上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係 試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢吸氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,呼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,吸氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,呼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.32,0:07:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,別繃著身體
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,別緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.20,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,對 望向天空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.45,0:08:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,讓四肢放鬆些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,別太用力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.10,0:08:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,讓四肢放鬆些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.48,0:08:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,放鬆些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.68,0:08:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,睜開眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.79,0:10:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,原來浮在水裡是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.28,0:10:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,這是用手拿著放的煙火？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,據說是東方之國的煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是米蘭老師搞來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,這個不危險嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,挺安全的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,公主殿下總是這麼說著卻幹些危險的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,明明能看到星星卻還要放煙火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅的國家不放煙火嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很少放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.05,0:12:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我聽說自古以來人們都是在歡慶時放煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待煙火呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,既然要玩煙火
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,拿來打架豈不是更好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.37,0:12:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那就開始吧
