Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.12,0:13:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,古蕾雅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我們之後幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,煙火也放完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.88,0:13:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,放煙火真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.11,0:13:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,明天就要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺還沒玩痛快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是把想做的事都做了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,然後就該一起睡覺了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.11,0:13:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天可努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我等這一刻等了好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.84,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,終於能穿上成對的睡衣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.16,0:14:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我好想和你一起睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對…不行 安
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一起迎接美麗的清晨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我都說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.73,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
